        <sponsor name-id="L000566">Mr. Latta</sponsor> (for
			 himself, <cosponsor name-id="T000193">Mr. Thompson of Mississippi</cosponsor>,
			 <cosponsor name-id="W000804">Mr. Wittman</cosponsor>, and
			 <cosponsor name-id="W000799">Mr. Walz</cosponsor>) introduced the following
			 bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HII00">Committee
			 on Natural Resources</committee-name>, and in addition to the Committee on
			 <committee-name committee-id="HAG00">Agriculture</committee-name>, for a period
